Firestrike awoke as he was brought out, jerking out of Autofires 
hand.  His rifle shooting to his hand immediatly as he saw the 
D.E.D members also firing, but not missing, as two shots hit 
bullseye in the middle of both thier heads knocking Dreadwind and 
Darkwing offline.  "Get them inside" he said to Autofire and 
Ragnus.  I will report to Megatron."
